quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,105,Kaom Noh jikheun sulet dum Rasul Han jitem kaboe watee Noh peugah
  26,106,Chedara jih Noh geukheun bak jih nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,107,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,108,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,109,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Bak Po dum alam upah lon ka na
  26,110,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,111,Jiseuot sigra peue tajak peugah Ek kamoe pateh nyan narit gata Nyang ikot gata cit awak reundah Rakan gata dum cit hina dina
  26,112,Geukheun boh hana nyang jeuet lon peugah Hana lon teupeue dum buet ureueng nyan
  26,113,Keunira gopnyan sideh bak Allah Meunyo tateupeue Po lon nyang kira
  26,114,Ureueng nyan teuma han jeuet lon keubah Han roe lon use ureueng meuiman
  26,115,Peuingat mantong dilon lon peugah Lon nyoe peuingat sagai nyang nyata
  26,116,Jikheun treuk boh ka bek le tapeugah Meunyo han taiem hai Noh digata Meurajam gata jinoe le bagah
  26,117,Kheun Noh Tuhanku pakri kaom lon Han jipateh lon jikheun beurakah
  26,118,Neubuka jalan keu lon nibak jih Neubri lon bak jih jinoe le beu glah Ngon dum rakan lon ureueng meuiman
  26,119,Teuma Noh lheueh nyan Kamoe peuleupah Ngon rakan gopnyan geu-ek lam kapai Nyang peunoh beukai dum ngon blah bicah
  26,120,Awak nyang tinggai laen nibak nyan Kamoe peukaram lam laot luah
  26,121,Atra nyan bandum sit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Dijih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,122,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah